text: The Producers () is a 2015 South Korean television series. It stars Kim Soo- hyun, Cha Tae-hyun, Gong Hyo-jin and IU. It was shown on KBS from May 15 to June 20, 2015. ==Characters== * Kim Soo-hyun as Baek Seung-chan * Cha Tae-hyun as Ra Joon-mo * Gong Hyo-jin as Tak Ye-jin * IU as Cindy ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:2010s South Korean television series debuts Category:2015 television series debuts Category:2015 establishments in South Korea Category:South Korean drama television series
